  "name": "Scorching Disarm",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p>\n<hr />\n<p>You make a weapon unbearable to hold. Attempt an Athletics check to Disarm a target creature. You don't need to have a hand free to make this Disarm attempt. If the Disarm attempt succeeds, the target takes @Damage[4d6[fire]] damage unless it drops the weapon, and on a critical success, it takes @Damage[4d6[fire]] damage and drops the weapon. If you're legendary in Athletics, this increases to @Damage[8d6[fire]] damage.</p>"
